    BEXTR, BLCFILL, BLCI, BLCIC, BLCMSK, BLCS, BLSFILL, BLSI, BLSIC, BLSMSK, BLSR, BOUND, BSF, BSR, BSWAP, BT, BTC, BTR, BTS, BZHI,
