    IDIV, IMUL, IN, INC, INS, INSB, INSW, INSD, INT, INTO,
    JO, JNO, JB, JC, JNAE, JNB, JNC, JAE, JZ, JE, JNZ, JNE, JBE, JNA, JNBE, JA, JS, JNS, JP, JPE, JNP, JPO, JL, JNGE, JNL, JGE, JLE, JNG, JNLE, JG,
    JCXZ, JECXZ, JRCXZ, JMP,
